===Proper noun===
'''Epirus'''
# aone of the 13 [[peripheries]] of [[Greece]]
# A region in northwestern Greece, and southern Albania (known as [[Northern Epirus]]).  It contains [[Arta]], [[Ioannina]], [[Preveza]] and [[Thesprotia]].

